# Firmware health monitoring framework for wireless drivers

config FW_HEALTH
	tristate "Firmware health monitoring and recovery framework"
	depends on RUST
	help
	  Lockless firmware health monitor for wireless drivers.
	  Provides automatic crash detection, recovery triggering,
	  and diagnostic logging.  All wireless drivers can
	  optionally link against this module.

	  When in doubt, say M.
